{
  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, the local similarity estimation module (LSEM) is used to locate the key points.",
    "In addition, in order to deal with the low overlap, the global estimation module (GSEM) is introduced to make the downsampling more concentrated in the overlap area.",
    "This module can find the corresponding points well with the twosided outlier removal mechanism based on multi-scale features.",
    "This method can extract and utilize the features of multi-scale point clouds well and avoid the interference of outliers.",
    "However, when the central region of the point cloud to be registered is difficult to distinguish, the registration accuracy of this method is faster."
  ]
}